profile:
Weed Man Montreal's General Manager Antoine Auray, has been part of the Weed Man family for the last 8 years. His background as a lawn care professional makes a huge difference in the quality of service the team delivers. His knowledge and drive to deliver excellent service are a must for anyone in his position. The residents of Montreal and surrounding areas have set the bar high for Antoine Auray, the franchise has been in the city for over 24 years.

Weed Man Montreal works together with their customers by offering a complete line of lawn care programs in combination with proper watering and mowing to provide the healthiest looking lawns possible. Throughout the years of exceptional performance, Weed Man Montreal has been exceeding the needs of their clients by providing the highest quality service in the industry and establishing their brand as one of the premier lawn care companies in the service area.
